    "title": {
      "rendered": "14 Must-Know Stats About Fundraising, Social Media, and Mobile Technology"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Must-Know-Fundraising-Stats-Square.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-16246\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"box_\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Must-Know-Fundraising-Stats-Square-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Must-Know-Fundraising-Stats-Square.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Must-Know-Fundraising-Stats-Square.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Must-Know-Fundraising-Stats-Square.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Must-Know-Fundraising-Stats-Square.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Must-Know-Fundraising-Stats-Square.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>Spring is report season in the nonprofit sector. A slew of <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2014/05/03/fundraisingreports/\">new data is released</a> and this year the emerging theme is that online fundraising is rapidly rising, especially on mobile devices. Nonprofits that have not yet adopted a mobile-first approach to online communications and fundraising can use the new data to help convince executive staff and board that a new <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2014/02/25/11-responsively-designed-nonprofit-websites-to-study-and-learn-from/\">mobile-compatible website</a> should be high on their priority list. Crowdfunding, peer-to-peer fundraising, monthly giving, and email fundraising is also proving to be effective, as you can read <em>and see</em> below.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>1. Responsive design doubles giving on mobile devices.</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"http://www.donordrive.com/blog/sneak-peak-of-our-white-paper-responsive-design-doubles-mobile-giving/#.U3jQb_ldXmc\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16094\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"mobile design doubles mobile giving\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-design-doubles-mobile-giving.png?resize=600%2C308\" width=\"600\" height=\"308\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-design-doubles-mobile-giving.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-design-doubles-mobile-giving.png?resize=300%2C154&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a>Source: <a href=\"http://www.donordrive.com/blog/sneak-peak-of-our-white-paper-responsive-design-doubles-mobile-giving/#.U3jQb_ldXmc\">DonorDrive</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> 2. Facebook refers 29.4% of traffic to donation pages<br />\non #GivingTuesday.</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.artez.com/blogs/digitalfundraisingfromatoz/prepare_for_year_end_donations_with_these_givingtuesday_mobile_and_s\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16206\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"GIVING TUES Facebook\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/GIVING-TUES-Facebook.png?resize=600%2C479\" width=\"600\" height=\"479\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/GIVING-TUES-Facebook.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/GIVING-TUES-Facebook.png?resize=300%2C239&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"http://www.artez.com/blogs/digitalfundraisingfromatoz/prepare_for_year_end_donations_with_these_givingtuesday_mobile_and_s\">Artez Interactive</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. Fifty-five percent of those who\u00a0engage with nonprofits via social media\u00a0have been inspired to\u00a0take further action.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://waggeneredstrom.com/what-we-do/social-innovation/report-digital-persuasion/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16226\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"donors-with-social-media (1)\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/donors-with-social-media-1.jpg?resize=600%2C335\" width=\"600\" height=\"335\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/donors-with-social-media-1.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/donors-with-social-media-1.jpg?resize=300%2C167&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"http://waggeneredstrom.com/what-we-do/social-innovation/report-digital-persuasion/\">Waggener Edstrom</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. For every 1,000 fundraising emails sent<br />\na nonprofit raises $17.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://mrbenchmarks.com/#infographic\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16213\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Benchmark Infographic\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Benchmark-Infographic.png?resize=600%2C302\" width=\"600\" height=\"302\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Benchmark-Infographic.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Benchmark-Infographic.png?resize=300%2C151&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"http://mrbenchmarks.com/#infographic\">M+R and NTEN</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. Monthly donors give 42% more in one-year than<br />\none-time donors.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.nonprofitmarketingblog.com/comments/new_infographic_why_recurring_giving_matters\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16208\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"monthly giving inforgraphic\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/monthly-giving-inforgraphic.png?resize=600%2C303\" width=\"600\" height=\"303\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/monthly-giving-inforgraphic.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/monthly-giving-inforgraphic.png?resize=300%2C151&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"http://www.nonprofitmarketingblog.com/comments/new_infographic_why_recurring_giving_matters\">Network for Good</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. Sixty-four percent of Millennials prefer to fundraise through walk/run/cycling events.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/MCON-nonprofits-fundraising1.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16516 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"MCON-nonprofits-fundraising\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/MCON-nonprofits-fundraising1.png?resize=600%2C235\" width=\"600\" height=\"235\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/MCON-nonprofits-fundraising1.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/MCON-nonprofits-fundraising1.png?resize=300%2C117&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Source: <a href=\"http://www.themillennialimpact.com/mcon14\">Millennial Impact</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">7. Walk/run/cycling event fundraisers who send more than 15 emails raise 76% more than non-email senders.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/p2p-fundraising-study-infographic\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16221\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"super emails senders\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/super-emails-senders.png?resize=600%2C314\" width=\"600\" height=\"314\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/super-emails-senders.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/super-emails-senders.png?resize=300%2C157&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/p2p-fundraising-study-infographic\">Blackbaud</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">8. The average nonprofit crowdfunding campaign<br />\nraises $9,237.55.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://craigconnects.org/crowdfundinginfographic\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16234\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"crowdfunding nonprofit\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/crowdfunding-nonprofit.png?resize=600%2C155\" width=\"600\" height=\"155\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/crowdfunding-nonprofit.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/crowdfunding-nonprofit.png?resize=300%2C77&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"https://craigconnects.org/crowdfundinginfographic\">craigconnects</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">9. Online giving grew 13.5% in 2013.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/charitablegiving-infographic#.U5G6z_ldXmc\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16211\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Online Giving Large 2013\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Online-Giving-Large-2013.png?resize=600%2C361\" width=\"600\" height=\"361\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Online-Giving-Large-2013.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Online-Giving-Large-2013.png?resize=300%2C180&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/nonprofit-resources/charitablegiving-infographic#.U5G6z_ldXmc\">Blackbaud</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>10. Ten percent of annual giving occurs on the last<br />\nthree days of the year.</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www1.networkforgood.org/digitalgivingindex\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16223\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"ten percent of all giving\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/ten-percent-of-all-giving.png?resize=600%2C441\" width=\"600\" height=\"441\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/ten-percent-of-all-giving.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/ten-percent-of-all-giving.png?resize=300%2C220&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"http://www1.networkforgood.org/digitalgivingindex\">Network for Good Digital Giving Index</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">11. Custom-branded donate pages nested inside a nonprofit&#8217;s website raise 6X more money.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www1.networkforgood.org/digitalgivingindex\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16229\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"oNLINE\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/oNLINE.png?resize=600%2C394\" width=\"600\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/oNLINE.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/oNLINE.png?resize=300%2C197&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www1.networkforgood.org/digitalgivingindex\">Network for Good Digital Giving Index</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">12. Sixty-four percent of donations are made by women.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/04/29/infographic-shows-charity-is-more-than-money_n_5233390.html?&amp;ncid=tweetlnkushpmg00000058\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16100\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Women donate more\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Women-donate-more.png?resize=600%2C285\" width=\"600\" height=\"285\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Women-donate-more.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Women-donate-more.png?resize=300%2C142&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/04/29/infographic-shows-charity-is-more-than-money_n_5233390.html?&amp;ncid=tweetlnkushpmg00000058\">Everyday Hero</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">13. Nonprofits share a daily average of 1.2 updates on Facebook and 5.3 tweets.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://mrbenchmarks.com/#infographic\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16215\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"average facebook posts facebook nonprofits\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/average-facebook-posts-facebook-nonprofits.png?resize=600%2C298\" width=\"600\" height=\"298\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/average-facebook-posts-facebook-nonprofits.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/average-facebook-posts-facebook-nonprofits.png?resize=300%2C149&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"http://mrbenchmarks.com/#infographic\">M+R and NTEN</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">14. Thirty percent of nonprofits are experimenting<br />\nwith Instagram.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.nonprofitmarketingguide.com/blog/2014/01/08/2014-nonprofit-communications-trends-report-infographic/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16232\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"experimenting with instagram\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/experimenting-with-instagram.png?resize=600%2C401\" width=\"600\" height=\"401\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/experimenting-with-instagram.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/experimenting-with-instagram.png?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong>Source: <a href=\"http://www.nonprofitmarketingguide.com/blog/2014/01/08/2014-nonprofit-communications-trends-report-infographic/\">Nonprofit Marketing Guide</a></strong></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-for-good-look-inside.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.<br />\n<strong> </strong></p>\n",
